<span id="an_11:36">11:36</span> Mekeratiten Hefer; Peloniten Ahija;

<span id="an_11:37">11:37</span> Hezro fra Karmel; Na'araj, Ezbajs Søn;

<span id="an_11:38">11:38</span> Joel, Natans Broder; Mibhar, Hagritens
