<span id="an_11:40">11:40</span> Ira fra Jattir; Gareb fra Jattir;

<span id="an_11:41">11:41</span> Hetiten Urias; Zabad, Alajs Søn;

<span id="an_11:42">11:42</span> Rubeniten Adina, Sjizas Søn, et af
